'''Tallera Downs''' was [[Nubia/Legends|Nubia's]] largest and most spectacular [[Ronto/Legends|ronto]] racing course. Located south of [[Nuba City]], it was two and a half [[kilometer]]s long and had seating for one hundred twenty thousand fans, and room for more in hovering luxury suites.   It featured rocky slopes, mud pits, and water hazards.  The Nuba City monorail had a station here, and the center of the track hosted a huge bazaar on race day. <ref name="Coruscant and the Core Worlds">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

The course was located south of [[Nuba City]], and it was here the [[Tallera Open]] contests were held.

